				<td colspan="2"><span>All skills are supposed to be (lvl+1)x5 with the exception of the untrainable Offense and Defense which are strictly lvl*5.
<br />

<br />
At lvl 21 your max skills are 100 for all languages (they are the exception to both rules), 110 for all trainable skills such as those you mention above, and 105 for Offense and Defense.
<br />

<br />
There is no need for a guide, the info is already out there.  Many times on this site as a matter of fact.</span></td>
