				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: Training trap and lock skills<a name="50908"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jul 9 04 10:43 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I highly doubt at level 21 it capped at 63. As Shas pointed out, the main formula is (level + 1)*5. It's been this way for years. With few exceptions. Like Rogues pick lock I believe can raise 2 points every level past 50 up to 55 where it caps at 210....
<br />

<br />
ex:
<br />
200 (up to and including 50)
<br />
ding 51, can now get lock pick to 202
<br />
ding 52, can now get lock pick to 204
<br />
ding 53, can now get lock pick to 206
<br />
ding 54, can now get lock pick to 208
<br />
ding 55, can now get lock pick to 210 (capped)
<br />

<br />
(this is for rogue only, not bard lock pick) I know this one cause I leveled my rogue to take to ssra with me for the doors there.
<br />

<br />
Look around the site.... use the search function.....  this site has tons to offer if you take the time to look</span></td>
